__data__.text: a kitchen with dark gray cabinets and light-colored countertops; a white refrigerator located in the corner of the room between two white walls and next to the cabinets; the countertop holding various food items including a jar of jam, a box of jello, and a box of salt; a sink with a faucet on the countertop to the right of the cabinets; a stove top with a pot on it; a range hood above the stove; a dining table with a light brown top and white chairs around it, located in a separate area from the kitchen; various items on the dining table including bottles, a box of crackers, and a glass; the floor made of dark wood parquet; white walls surrounding the kitchen and dining area.
